name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Typee - A Browser Command Line & Workflow Automation Tool

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Typee Browser Extension is keyboard first productivity tool that helps you interact with browser and AI faster and more efficiently.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Privacy First: There is no upfront permission to install Typee. You can precisely control what permission you want to use in permission page

Have you ever tried using keyboard only to finish you daily work with highest productivity?

Typee can help you via the Typee Command Line and Workflow! You can create your own command to fit your style.

Besides custom command, Typee has built-in commands out of box 
1. Tab management 
2. Tab Group management
3. Window management
4. Twitter Interactive
5. Alias Management
6. Expansion. Which automatically create alias. check the github for shared configurations

Quick Start Doc: https://typee.ez2.dev/

Any question can be asked on Discord https://discord.gg/vmDj8yWEPA
